v 3
d  Stata modules from the 2026 plausexog project
d
d  These modules extend Conley, Hansen, and Rossi's (2012)
d  "plausibly exogenous" framework -- originally implemented in
d  Damian Clarke's plausexog (SSC) for the 2SLS coefficient --
d  to additional target functionals.
d
p apexog    APE bounds for cfprobit under plausibly-exogenous IVs
